properties.Name: ShipmentStatusType
properties.Description:
A status type that may be applied to a Shipment.

Ex:
- Scheduled
- Released to Shipper
- Released to Carrier 
- In Transit
- Delivered to Ship-To Address
- At Consignee Location
- In Customs
- In Warehouse Storage
- In Quarantine
- Delayed
- Re-Routed
- Abandoned
- Unknown

Columns.Name: ShipmentStatusTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shipment Status Type.

Columns.Name: ShipmentStatusTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Shipment Status Type.

Columns.Name: ShipmentStatusTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Shipment Status Type.
